154
00:12:10,933 --> 00:12:15,515
After the quest starts, there is a split at the timing of the challenge.

155
00:12:15,515 --> 00:12:20,278
Here, not only do you proceed with the quest and proceed to the judgment,

156
00:12:20,278 --> 00:12:25,341
