187
00:14:07,992 --> 00:14:12,556
And the player would think that the choice was okay,

188
00:14:12,556 --> 00:14:15,118
and they would feel at ease,

189
00:14:15,118 --> 00:14:18,601
and they would think, I can play freely.

190
00:14:18,601 --> 00:14:20,182
I think that's an important mechanism.

191
00:14:21,773 --> 00:14:25,395
So in the flow of the last slide,

192
00:14:25,395 --> 00:14:27,636
if the player fails to move forward, he fails.

193
00:14:27,636 --> 00:14:29,517
And so he's given a hint, and he has

194
00:14:29,517 --> 00:14:30,918
scolded at the same time.

