00:14:52,585 --> 00:14:55,487
And when the player hears that kind of friendly response,

205
00:14:55,487 --> 00:15:00,149
it causes the player to feel okay, a little bit more comfortable, more in control,

206
00:15:00,149 --> 00:15:02,770
and hence this sense of freedom.

207
00:15:02,770 --> 00:15:03,731
And there's another trick in DP.

208
00:15:03,731 --> 00:15:09,574
