222
00:16:14,964 --> 00:16:23,669
So to recap this third point, we allow for a retry at any time, which makes the player

223
00:16:23,669 --> 00:16:27,791
feel like he isn't being forced and has some freedom.

224
00:16:27,791 --> 00:16:33,294
Then we agree with the player's actions 100%, and that causes the player to feel like his

225
00:16:33,294 --> 00:16:36,375
actions were approved, and that always feels good.

226
00:16:36,375 --> 00:16:38,236
Have the story allow for it, too.

227
00:16:38,236 --> 00:16:40,137
That's the third box here.

228
00:16:40,137 --> 00:16:41,638
Just having the story allow for it.

229
00:16:42,160 --> 00:16:57,548
